com.artemis.utils

Class Bag<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.artemis.utils.Bag<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - object type this bag holds
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImmutableBag<E>, Iterable<E>

    public class Bag<E>
extends Object
implements ImmutableBag<E>
    Collection type a bit like ArrayList but does not preserve the order of its entities, speedwise it is very good, especially suited for games.
    Author:
    Arni Arent

      • ensureCapacity

        public void ensureCapacity(int index)
        Check if an item, if added at the given item will fit into the bag.

        If not, the bag capacity will be increased to hold an item at the index.

        yeah, sorry, it's weird, but we don't want to change existing change behavior
